{"title_page": "List of UWF Fury Hour episodes", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''UWF Fury Hour'' episodes}}\n''[[Universal Wrestling Federation (Herb_Abrams)#Fury_Hour|UWF Fury Hour]]'' was an American [[professional wrestling]] [[television program]] that premiered October 1, 1990 on [[SportsChannel America]], then moved to [[Prime Ticket]] in 1992. \n\n[[ESPN2]] repackaged existing SportsChannel America and Prime Ticket episodes into a half-hour format in 1995.\n\n==Episode Guide==\n===SportsChannel America (1990-1991)===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! No.\n! Original air date\n! Main Event\n! Filming Location\n! Filming Date\n|-\n|1\n|October 1, 1990\n|[[Brian Blair]] vs. [[Dan Spivey]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|September 24, 1990\n|-\n|2\n|October 8, 1990\n|[[Billy Jack Haynes]] vs. [[Col. DeBeers]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|September 24, 1990\n|-\n|3\n|October 15, 1990\n|[[Paul Orndorff]] vs. [[Steve Williams (wrestler)|Steve Williams]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|September 24, 1990\n|-\n|4\n|October 22, 1990\n|[[Bob Orton, Jr.]] vs. [[Paul Orndorff]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|October 11, 1990\n|-\n|5\n|October 29, 1990\n|[[Ivan Koloff]] vs. [[Nikita Koloff]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|October 11, 1990\n|-\n|6\n|November 5, 1990\n|[[Billy Jack Haynes]] vs. [[Ken Patera]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|October 11, 1990\n|-\n|7\n|November 12, 1990\n|[[Billy Jack Haynes]] vs. [[Col. DeBeers]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|November 11, 1990\n|-\n|8\n|November 19, 1990\n|[[Ken Patera]] vs. [[Nikita Koloff]]\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|November 11, 1990\n|-\n|9\n|November 26, 1990\n|[[Cactus Jack]] and Jack Armstrong vs. [[David Sammartino]] and Jay Strongbow, Jr.\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|November 11, 1990\n|-\n|10\n|December 10, 1990\n|[[Cactus Jack]] vs. Jay Strongbow, Jr.\n|[[Reseda Country Club]]\n|December 6, 1990\n|-\n|11\n|December 17, 1990\n|[[Col. DeBeers]] vs. [[Louie Spicolli]]\n|[[Reseda Country C